      <section eId="sec_CCP-4626">
        <num>CCP 4626</num>
        <heading>Section </heading>
        <subsection eId="CCP-4626__subsec_1">
          <num>(1)</num>
          <content>
            <p>The reimbursement to a co-owner of the amount proven to be due the co-owner
for the payment of taxes on the property, and the expenses of preservation of the property.</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="CCP-4626__subsec_2">
          <num>(2)</num>
          <content>
            <p>The payment to a co-owner of the amount proven to be due the co-owner by
another co-owner who has received and retained the fruits and revenues of the property.</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <authorialNote marker="source">
          <p>Source: https://www.legis.la.gov/legis/Law.aspx?d=112048</p>
        </authorialNote>
      </section>
